src:
AP Top Entertainment News at 1:08 a.m. EST
07 Nov 2019, 05:00 by EndPlay
Ginsburg, in book, questions confidential #MeToo agreements
Chris Brown holds high-end yard sale at his Los Angeles home
A CGI James Dean is cast in new film, sparking an outcry
Halperin's 'How to Beat Trump' sells 502 copies in 1st week
Met Opera to hold celebration of Jessye Norman on Nov. 24
Family: France's Catherine Deneuve hospitalized with stroke
Billie Eilish, Lizzo, Dua Lipa, Cabello to perform at AMAs
'Fifty Shades' publisher Anne Messitte is leaving company
